title: Best of The Program | Guests: Megyn Kelly & Janice Dean | 2/17/21
description:
CNN is praising Biden’s early bedtime, while at a town hall, Biden brushed off China’s Uighur genocide and claimed we didn’t have a vaccine when he took office. Fox News’ Janice Dean joins as New York Gov. Andrew Cuomo blames his nursing home scandal on staff. Megyn Kelly joins to review the heartbreaking story of a 17-year-old “Jane Doe” whose life is being ruined over accusations of racism.
